18#include "Matrix.h"
19
20#include <cstdint>
21
22namespace ZXing {
23
24/**
25 * @brief Represent a tri-state value false/true/empty
26 */
27class Trit
28{
29public:
30 enum value_t : uint8_t {false_v, true_v, empty_v} value = empty_v;
31 Trit() = default;
32 Trit(bool v) : value(static_cast<value_t>(v)) {}
33 operator bool() const { return value == true_v; }
34 bool isEmpty() const { return value == empty_v; }
35};
36
37using TritMatrix = Matrix<Trit>;
38
39} // ZXing
